732574f-a.title: Pets - Donkey.
732574f-a.text:
Pets, Donkey: A donkey and a load of hay outside of stables on
the south side of East 24th Street, between Second and Third Aves. This
locality has long been known as a horse trading center, in fact ever since
the removal of the Bulls Head Tavern from the lower Bowery to the N.W.
oorner of Third Ave. and 24th Street.
January 25, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
